@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_txewop(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v1 = wp.sin((wp.abs(tmp + 0.94) * 0.54))
    v0 = (tmp - ((v2 + 0.51 * v1 + 0.10) / (v2 + 0.47 * tmp + 0.38)))
    v2 = wp.exp(wp.sin((v2 + 0.26 * tmp + 0.29)))
    v1 = ((wp.cos(tmp + 0.37) + wp.exp(v0 + 0.23)) / (wp.sin(tmp + 0.99) / v0))
    v1 = v1
    tmp = ((0.90 / 0.89) * v1)
    tmp = (0.43 - 0.93)
    data[tid] = v0
